}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "1244-01000907-50Z" is silkscreened on the board. This would seem to be an ''[[Edimax]]'' manufactured device...
===Router Special Features=== *3G/4G data sharing, AiCloud, AiDisK, *Printer server, Download Master, *Multiple SSIDs, Parental Control
===Specifications=== *Product Segment: N300 (300Mbps) *Antenna: 3x detachable antenna (9dBi) *Operating Frequency: 2.4 GHz *Ports: USB: 1x USB 2.0 :LAN: 4x FE (RJ45) for 10/100 BaseT for LAN :WAN: 1x FE (RJ45) for 10/100 BaseT for WAN *Button: WPS Button, Reset Button, Power Button *Power Supply: :AC Input : 110~240V (50~60Hz) :DC Output : 12V with max. 1A current *Dimensions: 179 x 128 x 28 mm (WxDxH) *Weight: 467 g
